    <main id="conteudo"><section class="page-hero"><div class="wrap page-hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span class="signal"></span>Frequently asked questions</p><h1>Straight answers about the app.</h1><p>What VeVolt does, what depends on third parties and how personal data is handled.</p>
  </div></section><section class="section"><div class="wrap faq-list"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Does VeVolt show official real-time availability?</summary><p>No. The app combines public data and community reports. Confirm critical information with the operator or on site.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I start or pay for charging through VeVolt?</summary><p>Not in this version. VeVolt does not control public chargers or process energy payments.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Does VeVolt show ads?</summary><p>There are no third-party ads, including on the Free plan.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Does Premium include VeVolt Condo?</summary><p>No. Premium is personal; Condo is a separate administrator plan. Invited residents join free.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Who processes subscriptions?</summary><p>Google Play exclusively. Users manage or cancel through their store account.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Where are my charging records stored?</summary><p>Personal records, vehicle data and profile photo remain on the device. Condo hub data is synchronized among participants.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which map and charger sources are used?</summary><p>VeVolt uses MapLibre/OpenFreeMap, Open Charge Map and OpenStreetMap-based Market results.</p></details></div></section><section class="cta-band"><div class="wrap cta-inner"><div><h2>Request access</h2><p>Send the same email used on Google Play. Once it is added to the tester group, the store link will allow installation.</p></div><div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href="/en/testers">Join the test</a><a class="button secondary" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=br.com.vevolt" rel="noopener">Open Google Play</a></div></div></section></main>
